quran[564]{c,v,t}:
  78,1,Ba hanyetsana ka eng
  78,2,Ka litaba tse molemo
  78,3,Tseo ba ke keng ba lumellana ka tsona
  78,4,"Ruri, haufi ba tla ruoa tsebo"
  78,5,Ruri! Ruri haufi ba tla ruoa tsebo
  78,6,Ha Re ea pharalatsa lefats’e
  78,7,Ra tsepamisa lithaba
  78,8,Re le hlotse ka bobeli
  78,9,Ra hlophisa boroko ho ba phomolo ea lona
  78,10,Ra hlophisa bosiu ho ba sekhurumetso
  78,11,Le mots’ehare hore e be molemong oa lona
  78,12,Ra aha maholimo a supileng kaholim’a lona
  78,13,Ra beha teng khanya e babatsehang
  78,14,Re ts’ollella lipula tsa melupe ho tsoa marung
  78,15,Re melisang lijothollo le meroho
  78,16,Le lirapa tsa makhasi a lipapetloa
  78,17,Ruri! Letsatsi la tharollo ke nako ea pallo
  78,18,Letsatsi leo ka lona Terompeta e tla letsoa; le tla phalla ka likete-kete
  78,19,Le leholimo le tla phetloa joalo ka ha e ka ho na le likhoro
  78,20,Lithaba li tla nyamela joalo ka mohuli
  78,21,Ruri! Lihele ke sebaka sa khaoletsi
  78,22,Lehae la baetsalibe
  78,23,Mooba tlang ho phela teng mengoaha
  78,24,"Moo ba ke keng ba latsoa letho le pholileng, kapa seno"
  78,25,"Kantle ho mokelikeli o belang, mokelikeli o mots’o, o nkhang, o serame se qhoalisang"
  78,26,Ele moputso o ba ts`oanetseng
  78,27,Hobane! ba ne ba sa ts`abe qoso
  78,28,Empa ba latola lits’upiso tsa rona ba re ke leshano
  78,29,Tsohle li ngoliloe bukeng ea tlaleho
  78,30,"Kahoo, latsoang litholoana tsa mesebetsi ea lona; ha ho kekeletso eo le tlang ho e nehoa, ntle le kahlolo.”"
  78,31,Ruri! Ho ba lokileng ho teng phethiso ea litabatabelo tsa bona –
  78,32,Lirapa tsa merara
  78,33,Le baroetsana ba es’ong ho amane le banna
  78,34,Le mepotjoana e khaphatsehang
  78,35,Kamoo ba ke keng ba utloa lipuo tsa mafeela le leshano; –
  78,36,"Moputso ho tsoa ho Mong`a hau, mpho e lekaneng, –"
  78,37,"Eena Mong`a maholimo le lefats’e, le tsohle tse lipakeng, Ea Tletseng Lereko: ha ho ope ea matla ho phehisana le Eena"
  78,38,"Letsatsi leo Khabariele le manyeloi a mang ba tlang ho ema ka mahlofo, ho se ea buang kantle ho thato ea Allah, ea tletseng lereko U tla bua se nepahetseng"
  78,39,"Letsatsing leo ‘nete e tla ba pepeneneng: kahoo, ea ratang, molese a retelehele ho Mong`a hae"
  78,40,"Ruri, Re le lemositse ka kotlo e haufinyane, letsatsi leo ka lona motho a tlang ho bona seo matsoho a hae a se rometseng nale; mohana-tumelo o tla re, “Sekhobo se be honna! Hoja ke ne ke lerole!” Ka lebitso la Allah, Ea Lereko, Mong`a hao"
  79,1,Ka manyeloi a qotsulang ka soto
  79,2,Le manyeloi a qotsulang ka makhethe
  79,3,Le manyeloi a potlakelang ho ea thomong
  79,4,Joale ha e ka a peisong
  79,5,A laolang liketsahalo
  79,6,Mohla letsatsi leo Terompeta e letsoang lekhetlo la pele
  79,7,E latela ka phethako
  79,8,Lipelo li tla be li khathatseile mohlang oo
  79,9,Mahlo a talimile fats`e
  79,10,"Ba re: “Eng! Re tla busetsoa maemong a rona a mathomo"
  79,11,Eng! – re ne re le masapo a bolileng?”
  79,12,"Ba re: “Ruri! Seo e tla be el e poelo ea tahlehelo.”"
  79,13,Ruri! E tla ba ka molumo o le mong feela
  79,14,Ba tla be ba tsohile
  79,15,Na pale ea Moshe ha es’o finyelle ho uena
  79,16,Bonang! Mong`a hau U kile A memetsa ho eena phuleng e halalelang ea Tuwa
  79,17,“Tsamaea o ee ho Faro –hobane Ruri! O tlotse meeli eohle –
  79,18,"U re ho eena: na u lakatsa ho hloekisoa sebeng"
  79,19,"Hore ke u tataisetse ho Mong`a hau, u tle u mo ts’abe?”"
  79,20,Eaba Moshe o mo bonts’a sesupo se seholohali
  79,21,Empa o ile a latola a nyefola
  79,22,"Ho feta mona a furalla, a tsitlallela nyefolong"
  79,23,"Eaba o khobokanya sechaba sa hae, a hooa"
  79,24,"A re: “ke Mong`a lona, ea phahameng ka ho fetisisang.”"
  79,25,Allah U ile a mo otla le hona ho mo etsa mohlala bophelong bona le ho Bo-tlang
  79,26,Ruri! Sena ke temoso ho mang le mang ea ts’abang Allah
  79,27,Eng! Na tlholeho ea lona e boima kapa tlholeho e boima ke’a leholimo? Le hlotsoeng ke Allah
  79,28,"Ebile o phahamisitse leholimo holimo-limo, a le neha taolo le phetheho"
  79,29,"Bosiu ba lona A le neha lefifi, ho bo khabisa A bo fa khanya"
  79,30,Le lefats`e A le pharalatsa
  79,31,A hlahisa metsi le makhulo holim’a lona
  79,32,Le ho tsepamisa lithaba
  79,33,Molemong oa lona le mehlape ea lona
  79,34,Kahoo mohla ho tlang sekhobo se seholohali
  79,35,Letsatsing leo motho a tlang ho hopola tsohle tseo a li sebelelitseng
  79,36,Le mollo o tla behoa pontseng ea bohle
  79,37,"Joale, ba ileng ba tlola meeli eohle"
  79,38,Ba ikhethela bophelo ba lefats’e lena
  79,39,Lehae la bona e tlabe e le Lihele
  79,40,"Hoba ileng ba bonts`a ts’abo ea ho ema kapel’a Mong`a bona mohla kahlolo, ba qobisa phefomoloho ea bona litakatsong tsa mafeela"
  79,41,Lehae la bona e tla ba Serapa (paradeisi)
  79,42,"Ba u botsa ka motsotso oo, – “Na nako ea teng e behiloeng e neng?”"
  79,43,Phatlalatso ea nako eo e o ama joang
  79,44,Ke Mong`a hau Ea tsebang motsotso le nako e behiloeng
  79,45,U mpa u le mohlokomelisi feela hoba nang le ts’abo
  79,46,"Mohlang ba tlang ho e bona, e tla ka hoja ba phetse bosiu bo le bong, kapa nako ea hoseng ho le hong"
  80,1,"A busa lifahleho, a furalla"
  80,2,Hobane ho ile ha tla monna oa sefofu ho eena
  80,3,Empa ke`ng se neng se ka u bolella hore mohlaope a ka hola
  80,4,"Kapa ho amohela temoso, le thuto ea mo atlehisa"
  80,5,Ha ele ea hopolang hore eena o ea ikhona
  80,6,Eena o mo thehela tsebe
  80,7,Le ha e le hore ha se molato oa hao ha a sa hole
  80,8,Empa haele ea tlileng ho uena ka boitelo
  80,9,Le ka ts’abo
  80,10,Ha u oa ka oa mo natsa
  80,11,Ruri sena ke temoso
  80,12,"Kahoo, lesa ea ratang ho e amohela, a e boloke khopolong"
  80,13,Kahar’a mangolo e ea hlompheha (al-lauh al-mahfuz)
  80,14,E phahame e hloekile e ea halalela
  80,15,Ka matsoho a bangoli
  80,16,"Ba hlomphehang ba hloekileng, ba toka"
  80,17,"Sekhobo se be ho motho, ke eng se entseng hore a latole Allah"
  80,18,O hlotsoe ka eng
  80,19,"Ka lerotholi la there: U mo hlotse, A mo matlafatsa ka hohle"
  80,20,Eaba U mo nolofaletsa tsela
  80,21,"A mo hlophela lefu, le ho patoa lebitleng"
  80,22,"Ka thato Ea Hae, U tla mo tsosa"
  80,23,Ha a phethisa seo Allah A mo laetseng sona
  80,24,Motho ha a ke a lemohe lijo tsa hae
  80,25,Kamoo Re nesang pula kateng
  80,26,Re petsolang lefats’e
  80,27,Re melisa lijo-thollo holim’a lona
  80,28,"Morara, le lijo tse ahang ‘mele"
  80,29,Mehloare le lipalema
  80,30,Le lirapa tse hlehleaneng ka lifate
  80,31,Le litholoana le lesere
  80,32,Ele nala molemong oa lona le mehlape
  80,33,Khabareng e tlare ho utloahala molumo o tabolang meropa ea tsebe
  80,34,Letsatsing leo motho a tla baleha ngoana’a bo
  80,35,‘Mae le ntata’e
  80,36,Mosali le bana ba hae
  80,37,"E mong le e mong letsatsing leo, o tla be a na le mats`enyeho a lekaneng ho tsotella e mong"
  80,38,"Letsatsing leo, lifahleho tse ling li tla ela"
  80,39,"Li ts’eha, li nyakalletse"
  80,40,Lifahleho tse ling tsona letsatsing leo li tla pulufala
  80,41,Li apareloe ke lefifi
  80,42,"Bao e tlabe e le balatoli ba Allah, baetsi ba tse mpe"
  81,1,Mohla letsatsi le timelang
  81,2,"Linaleli li oelang, li fifala"
  81,3,Lithaba li nyamela
  81,4,Li kamele tse ts`ehali tse emereng likhoeli li le leshome li lahluoe feela
  81,5,Liphoofolo tse hlaha li bokelloang ‘moho
  81,6,Mohla maoatle a belang
  81,7,Mephefomoloho e kopang’oang
  81,8,"Mohla lesea la ngoanana le tsetetsoeng le phela, le hlongoang lipotso –"
  81,9,Na u bolaetsoe sebe sefe
  81,10,Maqephe a manolloang
  81,11,Leholimo le arohang ka lehare
  81,12,Khanare ea mollo e qhomeletsoa
  81,13,Serapa se atametsoang haufinyane
  81,14,Phefomoloho ka ng`oe e tla tseba seo e se sebelelitseng
  81,15,Ruri ke bitsa ho linaleli ho paka
  81,16,"Topa, kapa ipate"
  81,17,Le ka bosiu ha bo esa
  81,18,Le ka meso ha e tebela lefifi
  81,19,Ruri! Lena ke lentsoe la morumuoa ea hlomphehang
  81,20,"Ea sitsitsoeng ka matla, le maemo kapel’a Mong`a Terone"
  81,21,"Ea hlonephehang, ea ts’epahalang"
  81,22,Molekane oa lona ha se lehlanya
  81,23,Ka ntle ho qeaqeo u ile a `monela sebakana
  81,24,Ha a pate tsebo ea tse sa bonoeng (li-jinn) ka soele
  81,25,Lena ha se lentsoe la Satane ea rohakehileng
  81,26,"Joale, le ea kae"
  81,27,Ruri ona ke molaetsa ho mafats`e ohle
  81,28,Molemong oa e mong le e mong oa lona ea ratang ho tsamaea ka nepo
  81,29,"Empa ha ho kamoo le ka ratang kantle ho thato ea Allah, – Allah `Maballi oa mafats`e. Ka lebitso la alla, Ea Lereko, Mong`a hao"
  82,1,Mohla leholimo le petsohang ka lehare
  82,2,Linaleli li hasanang
  82,3,Maoatle a tlolang meeli
  82,4,Mabitla a nyebekoloha
  82,5,Phefomoloho ka ng`oe e tla tseba seo e se rometseng nale le seo e se patileng
  82,6,Oho motho! Ke eng se o hohetseng ho tloha ho Mong`a hau Ea nala e Khaphatsehang
  82,7,"Ea U hlolileng, a U neha sebopeo A o fa lineo ka tekanyo"
  82,8,"Ka tsela e mokhahlang, A u bopa"
  82,9,Empa o latola tokelo le kahlolo
  82,10,Ruri! Ho tengba lebeli holim’a lona
  82,11,"Ba mosa ba hlomphehang,-ba ngolang"
  82,12,Ba tseba tsohle tseo le li etsang
  82,13,"Haele bohle ba lokileng, ba tla ba nyakallong"
  82,14,"Baetsalibe, – Ba tla ba kahar’a Mollo"
  82,15,Oo ba tla kena mohla Letsatsi la Kahlolo
  82,16,Ba ke ke ba o qoba
  82,17,Ke`ng se tla u hlalosetsa hore na Letsatsi la Kahlolo ke eng
  82,18,"Hape, ke`ng se tla u hlalosetsa hore na Letsatsi la Kahlolo ke eng"
  82,19,Ke letsatsi leo ka lona ho seng phefomoloho e tlang hoba le matla a ho thusa e ng`oe. Taelo letsatsing leo ke ea Allah
  83,1,Sekhobo se be holim’a baqhekanyetsi
  83,2,"Bao e reng ha ba amohela tekanyo ho batho, ba e batla e felletse"
  83,3,Empa ha ba lokela ho bekha ka tekanyo kapa ho bekhela batho; ba fana ka boima bo tlase
  83,4,Ha ba nahane hore ba tla biletsoa boikarabelong
  83,5,Mohla Letsatsi la Tonanahali
  83,6,Letsatsi leo batho ba tlang ho ema kapel’a Mong`a mafats’e
  83,7,Che! Ruri tlaleho ea baetsalibe e kahar’a sijjin –
  83,8,Keng se tla o hlalosetsa hore sijjin ke eng? –
  83,9,Tlaleho e ngoliloeng
  83,10,Sekhobo letsatsi leo se be ho ba latolang
  83,11,Ba latolang Letsatsi la Kahlolo
  83,12,"Leo ho seng ea ka le latolang ntle le motloli oa molao, moetsalibe"
  83,13,"Ha a pheteloa Lits’enolo tsa Rona, a re: “Lits’omo tsa mehleng ea khale.”"
  83,14,Che! Empa lipelong tsa bona ke mabali a tseo ba li etsang
  83,15,Ruri! Letsatsing leo ba tla siroa ho bona khanya e tsoang ho Mong`a bona
  83,16,Khabareng ba tla kena mollong oa Lihele
  83,17,"Ho tla thoe ho bona: “Sena ke nnete eo le e latotseng le re ke leshano!”"
  83,18,Ruri tlaleho ea ba lokileng e bolokiloe ‘iliyin –
  83,19,Keng se tla le hlalosetsa hore ‘iliyin ke eng
  83,20,Tlaleho e ngoliloeng
  83,21,E pakelang ba haufinyane le Allah
  83,22,Ruri ba lokileng ba tla ba nyakallong (paradeising)
  83,23,"Literoneng, ba tla talima lintho tsohle"
  83,24,U tla ba tseba ka khanya e phatsimang lifahlehong
  83,25,"Lenyora la bona le tla kholisoa ka seno sa morara, o bitieletsoeng"
  83,26,"Sekoahelo sa teng e tla ba “musk”: molemong oa sena ba lakatsang tlhonolofatso ha ba hahabelle teng"
  83,27,Ba tla e fuoa le motsoako oa tasnim
  83,28,Seliba seo ho noang ba atametseng haufi le Allah
  83,29,Baetsalibe ba ne ba tloaetse ho soma ba-kholoang
  83,30,Ha ba ne ba feta pela bona ba ne ba panyetsana
  83,31,"Nakong eo ba boelang ho mehahabo bona, ba khutla ba soma"
  83,32,"Ha ba ba bona, ebe ba re: “Bonang bana ke ba khelohileng Ruri.”"
  83,33,Empa ha ba ea romelloa ho ba balebeli ba bona
  83,34,Letsatsi leo ba-kholoang ba tla ts’eha mahana-tumelo
  83,35,"Literoneng, ba tla talima lintho tsohle"
  83,36,Na mahana-tumelo a ke keng a lefshoa ho latela liketso tseo a neng a li etsa
  84,1,Mohla leholimo le qhashohang ka lehare
  84,2,Le thea-tsebe ho Mong`a lona. Le tlamehile
  84,3,Ha lefats’e le batalatsoa
  84,4,"Le hlohlolla se ka hara lona, le sala le hlobotse"
  84,5,"Le thea-tsebe ho Mong`a lona, le tlamehile"
  84,6,"Oho motho! Ruri o khasetsa ho Mong`a hau, u khasa ka thata, – empa u tla kopana le Eena"
  84,7,Haele ea tla fuoa tlaleho ea hae ka letsohong la molema
  84,8,U tla be a tlaleha bobe
  84,9,"U tla retellehela ho ba habo, a thabile"
  84,10,Empa ea fuoang tlaleho ea hae ka morao
  84,11,O tla llela timelo
  84,12,O tla kena lelakabeng la mollo
  84,13,"Ruri! O phetse le beng ka eena, ka nyakallo"
  84,14,Ruri! O ne a nahana hore ha a na khutlela ho Rona
  84,15,"Che, che! Mong`a hae haesale a mo shalimme"
  84,16,Kahoo ke hlapanya ka mahlaseli a letsatsi ha le hlahlamela litaba
  84,17,Bosiu le tseo bo-ikapesitseng ka tsona
  84,18,"Le ka ngoeli, e tolokile"
  84,19,Le tla tsamaea sebaka le sebaka
  84,20,Molato ke’ng ka bona haele moo ba hloka tumelo
  84,21,"Ha ba balloa Qur`an, ba sa khumamele Allah"
  84,22,Empa mahana-tumelo a latola
  84,23,Empa Allah u na le tsebo e phahametseng ka tseoba li patang
  84,24,Kahoo u ba tsebise ka kotlo e bohloko
  84,25,"Kantle ho ba-kholoang, ba liketso tse lokileng; moputso oa bona oo ke keng oa thisa"
  85,1,Ka leholimo le linaleli tse jeroeng ke lona
  85,2,Ka le Letsatsi le Ts’episitsoeng
  85,3,"Ka ea pakang, le se pakoang"
  85,4,Ho malimabe baepi ba mokoti
  85,5,Mollo o beseletsoang
  85,6,Bona! ba ne ba tjamme pel’a ona
  85,7,Ke lipaki ho tseo ba neng ba li etsa khahlanong le ba-kholoang
  85,8,"Ba ba hlokofalitse kantle ho lebaka haese feela hore ba kholoa ho Allah, Ea Matla Oohle, U ts’oanetsoe ke Lithoriso tsohle"
  85,9,Eo `Muso oa maholimo e leng oa Hae le lefats`e! Allah ke Paki ea lintho tsohle
  85,10,"Haele ba hobosang ba-kholoang, banna le basali, ba sa retellehele ka boinyatso(ho Allah), ba tla fumana kahlolo ea Lihele: ba tla otloa ka mollo o tukang"
  85,11,"Ho ba-kholoang, ba etsang ketso tse lokileng, e tlaba lirapa tseo linoka li phallang tlasa tsona. Seo ke pholoho e babatsehang"
  85,12,Ruri letsoho la Mong`a hau le matla
  85,13,"Ke Eena Ea hlolang ho tloha mathomong, A boele A phete"
  85,14,"U ts’oarela ka mehla, U Tletse Lerato-le-Mohau"
  85,15,Mong`a Terone e Tlotlehang
  85,16,Moetsi oa tsohle tseo A li rerang
  85,17,Na pale ea mabotho e fihlile ho uena
  85,18,A Faro le a Ba – Thamud
  85,19,Empa mahana-tumelo a lula a latola
  85,20,Empa Allah U ba kopetse ka morao
  85,21,Che! Sena ke Qur`an e tlotlehang
  85,22,E ngoliloeng letlapeng e babaletsoeng
  86,1,Ka leholimo le moeti oa bosiu
  86,2,Keng se tla le hlalosetsa hore na moeti oa bosiu keng
  86,3,"Ke Naleli, e khanyang"
  86,4,Ha ho phefomoloho e hlokang molebeli
  86,5,Motho ha a nahane seo a hlotsoeng ka sona
  86,6,O hlotsoe ka lerotholi la there –
  86,7,Le kollang lipakeng tsa mahalapa le likhopo
  86,8,Ruri Allah U na le matla a ho mo phelisa
  86,9,Letsatsi leo liphiri li tlang ho utolloa
  86,10,Motho ha a na ba le matla kapa mothusi
  86,11,Ka leholimo le fanang ka pula
  86,12,Le ka lefats’e le petsohang
  86,13,Ruri! Lena ke lentsoe le arolang botle le bobe
  86,14,Ha se ntho ea papali
  86,15,"Haele bona, ba etsa morero"
  86,16,Le ‘Na ke loha leano
  86,17,Kahoo fana ka nyehlisetso ho mahana-tumelo; u ba fe phomolo ha nakoana
  87,1,"Tlotlisa lebitso la Mohlokomeli-Mong`a hau, Ea Okametseng Tsohle"
  87,2,"Ea hlotseng, Ea faneng ka taelo"
  87,3,"Ea hlomathitseng melao, Ea fanang ka tataiso"
  87,4,Ea hlahisang lekhulo
  87,5,Hamorao le fetohe lehlare
  87,6,"Ka mekhahlelo Re u ruta ho bala, hore u se ke oa lebala"
  87,7,"Kantle ho thato ea Allah, hoba U tseba tse pepeneneng le tse sephiring"
  87,8,Re tla nolofatsa tsela e u lebisang tseleng e otlolohileng
  87,9,"Ka hona fana ka keletso, ha keletso e le molemo"
  87,10,Keletso e tla amoheloa ke ba nang le ts’abo
  87,11,Empa e tla qobjoa ke ba malimabe
  87,12,Ba tlang ho kena Khanareng ea Mollo
  87,13,Oo kahara ona ba sa tlong ho shoa kapa ho phela
  87,14,Ba tla atleha ke ba itlhoekisang
  87,15,"Ba rorisa lebitso la Mohlokomeli-Mong`a bona, ka thapelo"
  87,16,"Che, le khetha bophelo ba lefats’e lena"
  87,17,"Empa bophelo Bo-tlang bo molemo, ha bo fele"
  87,18,"Ka sena se har’a mangolo a mathomo, –"
  87,19,Mangolo a Abrahama le Moshe
  88,1,Na nalane ea timelo e ile ea u fihlela
  88,2,Lifahleho tse ling li tla phoqeha mohla tsatsi leo
  88,3,"Li be mats’oenyehong, li tepelle, –"
  88,4,Li kene lelakabeng la Mollo
  88,5,"Khabareng ba fuoe metsi, a belang ho noa, ho tsoa Selibeng se belang"
  88,6,"Ha ba na ho fumana lijo, haese litholoana tse babang"
  88,7,"Tse sa tlong ho aha ‘mele, kapa ho khorisa"
  88,8,Lifahleho tse ling li tla nyakalla mohla oo
  88,9,Ke thabo ho latela ts’ebetso ea bona
  88,10,Serapeng se phahameng
  88,11,Moo ba ke keng ba utloa lipuo tse hlohlonts’ang litsebe
  88,12,Moo Seliba se kopotsang
  88,13,Moo Li-Terone tse phahameng li leng teng
  88,14,Mepotjoana e behiloeng
  88,15,Mesangoana e behiloeng ka mekhahlelo
  88,16,Le meseme e nonofetseng
  88,17,Ha ba bone kamoo likamele li hlotsoeng
  88,18,Kamoo leholimo le phahamisitsoeng
  88,19,Le kamoo lithaba li tsepamisitsoeng
  88,20,Le kamoo lefats’e le aliloeng
  88,21,"Kahoo ba hlomekomelise, hobane u mohlokomelisi"
  88,22,Ha u molebeli oa litaba tsa bona
  88,23,"Empa ha mong a furalla, a latola Allah"
  88,24,Allah u tla mo ahlola ka kotlo e boima
  88,25,Poelo ea bona e ho Rona
  88,26,"Ho ho Rona, ho ba biletsa maikarabellong"
  89,1,Ka meso
  89,2,Le ka masiu a leshome
  89,3,Le ka libopuoa tsohle tsa Allah
  89,4,Le ka bosiu ha bo esa
  89,5,Holim’a lits’upiso tsena ho teng bopaki ho ba utloisisang
  89,6,Na ha u elelloe kamoo Mong`a hau A ileng A sebetsa kateng ka morabe oa Ba-Ad
  89,7,"Ba motse oa Iram, ka lits’ia tse phahameng"
  89,8,Bao ho es’ong ho be le tlholeho e ts’oanang le’a bona lefats’eng
  89,9,Joaloka morabe oa Ba – Thamude o ileng oa betla majoe kahar’a phula
  89,10,"Le Faro, Morena oa Lipalo"
  89,11,Bao kaofela ha bona ebileng batloli ba meeli eohle holim’a lefats’e
  89,12,Le hona ho fehla lehloeo kahar’a tsona
  89,13,Mong`a hau U ile A ts’ollela sekhobo sa kahlolo ea Hae holim’a bona
  89,14,Ruri! Ha ho se patehileng ho Mong`a hau
  89,15,"Joaloka motho eo ereng ha Mong`a hae A mo leka ka ho mo neha hlompho, A bile A ba lereko malebana le eena, e be o re: “Mong`a ka U mphile hlompho.”"
  89,16,"Empa hang ha A mo neha teko ka ho khutsufatsa mekhoa ea bophelo ba hae, o re: “Mong`a ka U ntlontlolotse.”"
  89,17,Che! Empa lona le hloloa ho hauhela khutsana
  89,18,Ha le khothaletsane phepo ea mafutsana
  89,19,Le ja mafa lekemekeme ka bonyollo bohle
  89,20,Le bile le rata leruo ka lerato le hlollang
  89,21,Che! mohla lefats’e le fetohang lehlohlojane le thumisehileng
  89,22,Mong`a hau A theoha le manyeloi a entse mekhahlelo ka mekhahlelo
  89,23,"Le lihele li atametsoa haufinyane; Ruri! Ke mohla motho a tlang ho hopola, empa mohopolo oo o tla mo thusa kang"
  89,24,"Motho o tla re: “Ao! Hoja ke mpile ka etsa letsete molemong oa bophelo ba ka!”"
  89,25,Ruri! O tla ahloloa ka kahlolo es’o kang e bonoa mohla letsatsi leo
  89,26,Ebile ha ho ea tlamang kamoo A tlamang kateng
  89,27,"Ho tla thoe hoba lokileng: “Oho lona! Meea ea lona ha e ke e phomole ka khotso"
  89,28,Khutlelang ho Mong`a lona le khotsofetse monyakeng o molemo oa Hae
  89,29,Kenang kahar’a makhabunyane a Ka
  89,30,Kahar’a serapa sa Ka!”
  90,1,Ke hlapanya ka motse-moholo ona (Makka) –
  90,2,Le uena u molokolohi oa motse-moholo ona –
  90,3,U motsoali le ngoana
  90,4,Ruri! Re hlotse motho hore a sebetse a fufuleloe
  90,5,Ha a nahane hore ha ho ope ea nang le matla holima hae
  90,6,"Mohlomong a ka re: “Ke harintse leruo le leholohali!”"
  90,7,Ha a nahane hore ha ho ope ea ‘monang
  90,8,Na ha se Rona ba mo sitsitseng ka mahlo a mabeli
  90,9,Le leleme le lipounama tse peli
  90,10,Le ho `montsa litsela tse peli
  90,11,Empa ha a potlakela tseleng e moepa –
  90,12,Ke`ng se tla le hlakisetsa na tsela e moepa ke`ng? –
  90,13,Ho neha lekhabunyane bolokolohi
  90,14,Kapa ho fana ka lijo matsatsing a tlala
  90,15,Ho khutsana ea leloko la hau
  90,16,Kapa ho mofutsana ea tlaleng ea boja-likata
  90,17,"Ka hona a tlaba har’a ba-kholoang, a khothaletsa ho ba le mamello le ho khothaletsa ho ba mosa le kutloelo bohloko"
  90,18,Bao ke balekane ba tla ba letsohong la molema
  90,19,"Empa haele ba latolang Lits’upo tsa Rona, ke balekane ba letsoho la ntsohohlo"
  90,20,Mollo e tla ba sekhele sa bona
  91,1,Ka letsatsi le khanya ea lona
  91,2,Ka ngoeli e le latelang
  91,3,Ka lets`eare ha le bontsa mahlaseli
  91,4,Ka bosiu ha bo le koahela
  91,5,Ka motheo oa leholimo le sebopeho sa lona
  91,6,Ka lefats’e le bophar`a ba lona
  91,7,Ka phefumoloho le tekanyetso le taelo eo e filoeng
  91,8,Le tataiso khethollong ho se setle le se sebe
  91,9,Ruri! Ea atlehang ke ea itlhoekisang
  91,10,Ea sa atleheng ke ea its’ilafatsang
  91,11,Ba-Thamude ba ile ba koeneha ka mekhoa ea bona e nyonts`ang
  91,12,"Bonang, monna oa moetsalibe ka ho fitisisa har’a bona o ile a khethoa"
  91,13,"Eaba moromuoa oa Allah o re ho bona: “Ke kamele ea Allah, kahoo e leseng e noe!”"
  91,14,"Empa ba ile ba mo nyelisa ba e bolaea, eaba Allah U oa ba ripitla ho latela sebe sa bona le hona ho siea malapa a bona ele masupi"
  91,15,Ha A na ts’abo ea litlamorao tsa teng
  92,1,Ha ho shoalana
  92,2,Le ha letsatsi le chaba
  92,3,Le ka Ea hlotseng monna le mosali
  92,4,Ruri! Liketso tsa hau li fapane
  92,5,Haele ea fanang le ho ts`aba Allah
  92,6,Le ho lumela ho se lokileng
  92,7,Re tla ba nolofaletsa tsela e lebisang boemong bo nepahetseng
  92,8,Empa ea khoaelang le ho inahana e le maikhona
  92,9,A latola se lokileng
  92,10,Re tla nolofatsa tsela e mo lebisang bothateng
  92,11,A maruo a hae a ka mo pholosa nakong eo a timelang
  92,12,Ruri! Ts’ebetso ea Rona ke ho fana ka tataiso
  92,13,Hobane Ruri! Qalo le qetello kea Rona
  92,14,Ke le lemositse ka lelakabe la mollo
  92,15,Ha ho ea tla cha teng ntle feela le ea qoetseng sebeng
  92,16,Ba latotseng le hona ho kheloha
  92,17,Haele ba lokileng ba tla o qoba
  92,18,Ba fanang ka leruo la bona hore ba tle ba hloeke moeeng
  92,19,Likelellong ba sa lebella molemo oa moputso ho tla ho bona
  92,20,Empa e le hona ho tsomana le sefahleho sa Mong`a bona Ea Phahameng ka ho fetisisa
  92,21,Haufinyana ba tla fumana khotsofalo
  93,1,Ka khalalelo ea khanya ea mats`a
  93,2,Le ka bosiu nakong eo bo es’ong ho se ts’ekhe
  93,3,Hore Mong`a hau ha A es’o u lahle kherehloa le hona ho u hloea
  93,4,Bophelo Bo-tlang bo tla ba molemo ho uena ho feta ba lefats’e
  93,5,Mong`a hau U tla u neha tsohle tse molemo hore u tle u khotsofale
  93,6,"Na ha se eena ea u fumaneng u le khutsana, a u lopolla"
  93,7,"Na ha se Eena Ea u fumaneng u ntse u phaqola, A u tataisa"
  93,8,"Na ha se Eena Ea u fumaneng u hloka letho, A u ruisa"
  93,9,"Ka lebaka leo, u se hatelle khutsana"
  93,10,Le hona ho leleka mokopi
  93,11,U phatlalatse nala ea Mong`a hau
  94,1,Na ha se Rona ba atollotseng sefuba sa hau
  94,2,Ra u imulla moroalo
  94,3,O neng o u roba mokokotlo
  94,4,Le hona ho tumisa boemo ba hau
  94,5,Ruri! Ho teng topollo mathateng ohle
  94,6,Ruri! Mathateng oohle ho teng topollo
  94,7,"Kahoo, ha u lopolotsoe, tsitlellela ho sebetsa ka thata"
  94,8,U retellehele ho Mong`a hau
  95,1,Ka Feikha le Olive
  95,2,Le ka Thaba ea Sinai
  95,3,Le ka motse o ts’ireletsong
  95,4,Ruri! Re hlotse motho ka tlholeho e babatsehang
  95,5,Eaba Re mo kokobetsa ka boemo bo tlase-tlase
  95,6,"Ntle le feela ea kholoang a etsa liketso tse lokileng, bao moputso oa bona o ke ke oa sitoa"
  95,7,Ke eng joale se ka o emang pele malebana le kahlolo
  95,8,Na ha se Allah Moahloli Ea Seli
  96,1,Bala! Ka lebitso la Mong`a hau Ea hlotseng
  96,2,Ea hlotseng motho ka lehloele la mali
  96,3,Bala! Mong`a hau U lereko le fetisisang
  96,4,Ea rutang ho ngola ka pene
  96,5,O rutile motho seo a sa se tsebeng
  96,6,Che! Empa motho o tlola meeli
  96,7,Ka ho nahana hore ke maikhona
  96,8,Ruri! Poelo ea tsohle e ho Mong`a hau
  96,9,Na o kile oa bona ea sitisang
  96,10,Lekhabunyane nakong eo le rapelang
  96,11,Na u kile oa bona ebang o its’etlehile tataisong
  96,12,Kapa o khothaletsa hoba mosa
  96,13,"Na o kile oa bona ebang u latola tataiso `nete, o oa furalla"
  96,14,Na ha a elelloe hore Allah U’a bona
  96,15,"Ha a hlokomele! ha a sa khaotse, re tla mo tutla ka qoba ea moriri –"
  96,16,"O leshano, o bile o silafetse –"
  96,17,"Joale, ha a bitse bathusi ba hae"
  96,18,Re tla bitsa manyeloi a kahlolo
  96,19,Se ka mo natsa. Empa u ithapalatse le hona ho ba haufinyane le Allah
  97,1,Ruri! Qura’n Re e senotse ka bosiu ba matla
  97,2,Ke eng se tla le hlalosetsa hore na bosiu ba matla ke eng
  97,3,Bosiu ba matla bo molemo ho feta likhoeli tse sekete
  97,4,Ke nako eo manyeloi le Khabariele ba theohelang lefats’eng ka tumello ea Mong`a bona le ka melao eohle
  97,5,Khotso!... Sena Ho fihlela chabo ea letsatsi
  98,1,"Haele ba latolang har’a Batho ba Lengolo le har`a ba hedene, ba ne ba ke ke ba sokoloha ho fihlela sesupo se hlakileng se finyeletse ho bona"
  98,2,"Sa moromuoa ea tsoang ho Allah, ea balang maqephe a hloekileng"
  98,3,"A jereng melao e nepahetseng, e topileng"
  98,4,Batho ba Lengolo ba ne ba ke ke ba arohana ho fihlela kamor’a hoba sesupo se hlakileng se finyelle ho bona
  98,5,"Ba ne ba laetsoe ho sebeletsa Allah le ho boloka tumelo ea bona e hloekile malebana le Eena, e be batho ba topileng ka tlholeho le hona ho phethahatsa lithapelo le ho fana ka linyehelo. Seo ke tumelo ea ‘nete"
  98,6,"Haele ba latolang har’a batho ba Lengolo le har`a bahedene, ba tla eba mollong-oa-lihele ho phela teng. Ke libopuoa tse nyonts’ang"
  98,7,"Bohle ba-kholoang, ba etsa liketso tse lokileng, – bona ke libopuoa tse molemo"
  98,8,"Moputso oa bona o ho Allah: lirapa tsa Edene, tseo linoka li phallang tlas’a tsona, ba tla phela teng kahosafeleng. Allah U tla nyakalla ke bona le bona ba tla nyakalla ke Eena. Tsena li molemong oa ba ts’abang Mong`a bona"
  99,1,Ha lefats’e le sisingoa la mathetho
  99,2,Le itlhohlolla moroalo
  99,3,"Motho o tla re: “Molato ke eng ka lefats’e”"
  99,4,Ke mohla lefat’se le tla bolela nalane ea lona
  99,5,Hobane Mong`a hau U tla le susumetsa
  99,6,Mohlang oo batho ba tla nyolosa ba theosa ka mekhahlelo ho ea bonts’oa liketso tsa bona
  99,7,Mong le mong ea etsang ketso e lokileng e fokolang sa ntoana- la-botsikoane o tla e bona
  99,8,Mong le mong ea etsang sebe le ha se ka fokola sa ntoana-la- botsikoane o tla se bona
  100,1,"Ka lipitsi tse mathang, tse hemeselang"
  100,2,Tseo maotong a tsona ho qobang litlhase
  100,3,Tse tsometsang tlhaselo ka matjeke
  100,4,E be li tsosa leroele khabong
  100,5,Li parola lebotho la lira ka lehare e le ngatana ng’oe
  100,6,Ruri! Motho o hloka teboho ho Mong`a hae
  100,7,E bile ke paki holim’a seo
  100,8,O lehala leratong la leruo
  100,9,Na ha a tsebe hore mohla mabitla a hlatsang likateng
  100,10,Se ka lifubeng tsa batho se tla behoa pepeneneng
  100,11,Letsatsing leo Mong`a bona U tlabe A tseba tsohle tsa bona
  101,1,Sekhobo
  101,2,Sekhobo ke eng
  101,3,Ebe ke eng se tla le tsebisa hore na sekhobo ke eng
  101,4,Ke letsatsi leo batho ba tla hasana joaloka lirurubele
  101,5,Lithaba li tla ba joalo ka boea
  101,6,Bao liketso tsa bona li tla imela sekala
  101,7,Ba tla phela bophelo ba nyakallo
  101,8,Empa eo liketso tsa hae li tla fokola sekaleng
  101,9,Lehae la hae e tla ba Lihele
  101,10,E be ke eng se tla le tsebisa hore na lihele ke eng
  101,11,Ke mollo o hlenneng
  102,1,Phehisano ea pokello ea matlotlo e le khelositse
  102,2,Ho fihlela le etela mabitleng
  102,3,Che! Haufinyane le tla tseba
  102,4,Hape le tla tseba
  102,5,Che! Hoja le na le tsebo e tehileng
  102,6,Hobane le tla bona mollo oa Lihele
  102,7,Hape le tla o bona ka tiieo
  102,8,Letsatsing leo le tla botsoa khahlano le monyaka oa lefats’e lena
  103,1,Ka Nako
  103,2,Ruri! Motho o tahlehong
  103,3,"Kantle ho ba-kholoang, ba etsang liketso tse lokileng, ba khothalletsang ‘nete le ba nang le mamello"
  104,1,Sekhobo se be ho moqabanyi e mong le e mong le raleshano
  104,2,Ea khobokantseng leruo la lefats’e lena le ho le bala
  104,3,O nahana hore leruo la hae le tla etsa hore a phele kahosafeleng
  104,4,Che! Ruri! O tla tjebeloa mollong o harinyang
  104,5,E be ke eng se tla le tsebisa hore mollo o harinyang
  104,6,Ke mollo oa Allah U hotelitsoeng
  104,7,Oo qhomelang holim’a lipelo tsa batho
  104,8,Ruri! o tlaba kupetsa
  104,9,Kahar’a lits’iea tse otlolotsoeng
  105,1,Na ha u ea bona kamoo Mong`a hau A ileng A ripitla balekane ba tlou kateng
  105,2,Ha A ka A nyopisa morero oa bona
  105,3,A romella mohlape oa linonyana khahlano le bona
  105,4,Ho ba furuletsa ka majoe a lenyetana
  105,5,A ba fetola lehlare
  106,1,Ka selekane sa Ma-Qureysh
  106,2,Re ile Ra etsa hore ba simolle maeto mariha le lehlabula
  106,3,Ha ba khumamele Mong`a ntlo ena
  106,4,Ea ba fepang khahlanong le tlala le ho ba sireletsa matsoalong a bona
  107,1,U kile oa bona motho ea latolang kahlolo
  107,2,Ke ea lelekang khutsana
  107,3,Ea sa khothaletseng ho feptjoa ha mafutsana
  107,4,Aa! Sekhobo se be holim’a barapeli
  107,5,Ba sa tsotelleng thapelo ea bona
  107,6,Ba etsetsang ho bonoa
  107,7,Ba hana ka litokelo tsa boahisane
  108,1,Ruri Re u nehile tlotla ea Seliba Paradeising
  108,2,"Kahoo, retelehela ho Mong`a hau ka thapelo, u etse sehlabelo"
  108,3,Ruri! Ke sera sa hau se tlang ho hloka bokamoso
  109,1,"E re: “Oho lona mahana-tumelo"
  109,2,Ha ke khumamele seo le se khumamelang
  109,3,Le lona ha le khumamele seo ke se khumamelang
  109,4,Ha nkeke ka khumamela seo le se khumamelang
  109,5,Etsoe le ke keng la khumamela seo ke se khumamelang
  109,6,"Tumelo ea lona ke ea lona, ea ka ke ea ka"
  110,1,Ha thuso le tlholo ea Allah li fihlang
  110,2,U bona lichaba li inehela tumelong ea Allah ka mekhopi
  110,3,"Keteka lithoriso tsa Mong`a hau, kopa ts’oarelo ho Eena: ke Eena Ea amohelang boinyatso, Ea Ts`oarelang"
  111,1,Ha mats`oho a Lahab a timele! Ha a timele
  111,2,Ha ho moputso maruong a hae le ho tseo a li bokellelitseng
  111,3,Haufi o tlaba mollong o khanare ea lelakabe
  111,4,Mohatsa`e o tla roala patsi e le libeso
  111,5,Thapo e lohiloeng ka makhapetla a palema e haretsoe molaleng oa hae (mohatsae)
  112,1,"E re: Ke Allah, Ea Inotsi"
  112,2,"Allah, Rabosafeleng"
  112,3,"Ha A tsoale, ha A tsoaloa"
  112,4,Ha ho ea ts’oanang le Eena
  113,1,"E re: Ke kopa ts’ireletso ho Mong`a meso"
  113,2,Khahlanong le tse silafetseng tse hlotsoeng
  113,3,Ka ho ts’oana le tse silafetseng tsa lefifing le noelletseng
  113,4,Le khahlanong le bobe ba balohi ba mafito
  113,5,Le khahlanong le bobe ba bahonuhi ha ba honoha
  114,1,"E re: ke kopa ts’ireletso ho Mong`a batho bohle"
  114,2,Morena oa batho
  114,3,Mopi oa batho
  114,4,"Khahlanong le linyonts`a tsa mosebi ea soto, ea hoeshetsang a be a nyamele"
  114,5,Ea silafatsang lipelo tsa batho
  114,6,Har’a masabonoeng (li-jinn) le har`a batho